title: Pixar
description:
Pixar Short Film DVD Collection

Pixar Short Films Collection (DVD Volume 1 released by Buena Vista Home Entertainment October 2007, DVD Volume 2 was released by Walt Disney Studios Home Entertainment November 2012)
Volume 1 has 13 short films and Volume 2 has 12 short films PLUS includes 7 student films (from Pixar's directors as a bonus feature).
33 short films in total (the last student film is .. well .. a little trippy ;)

Pixar films in MP4 format - Video 720p@1500kbps - Audio 48K@160kps Stereo -
Student films in MP4 format - Video & Audio unaltered -

- Covers & Wikipedia info included -
